nodes.text: Prengalli were water-dwelling creatures that could be found on the swampy planet of Artiod Minor, in the Morellian Commonwealth. The sentient natives of Artiod Minor, the Artiodacs, raised schools of prengalli in their aqua-farms.
Prengalli were first mentioned in Star Wars: Aliens of the Galaxy, a reference book written by Jason Fry and released on August 23, 2016.
